	<p><font face="arial, helvetica" size="2">It's been a while, but I don't think you need any kind of faction check to kill black dire, nor do you need to converse with him.  Once he is spawned, all you have to do is kill him.<br />
<br />
To spawn him, you have to kill the Advisor inside the castle.<br />
<br />
